┌ DisplayInfo
  ΞStudentRecord
  ΞSubjectRecord
  studentInfo!: ID → NAME → PROGRAM
  subjectInfo!: ID ⇸ COURSE → ℕ ⇸ ℕ ⇸ GRADE ⇸ 𝔸
